extends layout

block content
    article(class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8")
      div(class="lg:col-span-2")
        h1(class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2") Recent project: The October Lab
        p I've recently gotten to a stopping point with my IT lab I've began in late September 2025.
        p The lab features a myriad of technologies related to infrastucture and security.
        p For example, I would like to tighten the allowed hosts for SSH and to swap out the core routers with more powerful ones so I can get DMVPN phase 3 to function better.
        p In the future I plan to implement more security and to document it on here.

        p(class="pt-10") You can view the details on the project in the link below: 
        a(href="/it-lab-october-lab-2025" class="inline-block px-5 py-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 mr-3 mt-2") The October Lab

        p(class="pt-10") You can view the LinkedIn version of the details on the project in the link below: 
        a(href="https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/october-lablinux-glbp-ipsec-dmvpn-nat-ebgp-ospf-eigrp-terrance-ford-t5ere/" target="_blank" class="inline-block px-5 py-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 mt-2 mr-3") LinkedIn Version: The October Lab

